you're the only kid on the block
with one of these.

116
00:08:14,265 --> 00:08:16,900
Mom, is Dad
from another planet?

117
00:08:16,966 --> 00:08:19,902
- Who told you that?
- The kids say it at school.

118
00:08:19,966 --> 00:08:23,336
