- I don't know. Let me see.

151
00:10:05,099 --> 00:10:07,167
Hmm.

152
00:10:07,232 --> 00:10:09,667
You know,
I think you do.

153
00:10:11,933 --> 00:10:14,335
Mmm.

154
00:10:14,399 --> 00:10:16,200
Good night, sweetie.

155
00:10:16,265 --> 00:10:19,334
