in space exploration?

171
00:11:11,132 --> 00:11:13,901
- Well... none of them.
- I don't believe that.

172
00:11:13,966 --> 00:11:16,935
What about
the Venus Mariner?
They're launching next fall.

173
00:11:16,999 --> 00:11:19,668
